Version: 0.1-1
Depends: +libc +USE_EGLIBC:librt +USE_EGLIBC:libpthread +libubus +libuci
Menu-Depends: 
Provides: 
Section: net
Category: Network
Title: Check Internet and interface connectivity
Maintainer: Bruno Randolf <br1@einfach.org>
Source: pingcheck-0.1.tar.gz
Type: ipkg
Description: Checks by using "ping" (ICMP echo) wether a configured host (normally on the
internet) can be reached via a specific interface. Then makes this information
available via ubus and triggers "online" and "offline" scripts.
Bruno Randolf <br1@einfach.org>
